{"id":688879,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/688879.html","date":"2022-10-26T05:56:35Z","modified":"2022-10-31T18:35:28Z","title":"【404文库】晖诚勿思｜今天继续让大家看到西宁网友的心声","content":"<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>今天继续让大家看到西宁网友的心声<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>小晖<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/uE9RCQadjHmHUH5kZygP7g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微信公众号“晖诚勿思”</a><br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2022.10.25<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/过度防疫\" target=\"_blank\">过度防疫</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>想了想，我还是继续发表一些西宁朋友的心声，因为看得实在太让人心痛了，我无法不写出来。</p>\n<p>比如有西宁网友说了这样一件事，说去世前连个饱饭也没吃上。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/e9506c10.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是那个网友提供的截图。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/c2d0595d.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/569e46e3.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/27617e70.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>就在今天，西宁的鸡蛋又涨价了，一块七毛钱一个。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/96c115f6.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>还有西宁网友看到了这样一件事。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/3a422a23.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>西宁的农民工兄弟也很苦。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/fa34e70a.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>另一个新生妈妈的家属也在说出自己的心声。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/7f10e950.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是一个高二女生发给我的话。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/bd76000e.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>其实西宁网友的要求真的不多，只想自己的心声能被听到。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/225e02d0.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是一个普通务工者网友的心声。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/9515d24f.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>一个家长也很焦急。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/cd00e6ab.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>现在西宁的白菜都这么贵了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/3dccbb4c.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/980c9e3c.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是花菜的价格。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/b619f16f.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是蔬菜包的价格。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/bd12df44.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是另一个网友的遭遇。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/fa5fe773.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>还有网友的家门被锁上了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/51f051c4.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>就算回到小区，也不让进。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/6e477029.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>在西宁从事校外培训的网友也很苦。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/58236d53.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有网友就今天上午西宁的停水，发表了这样的感想。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/1a63e17f.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这是一个高三网友的心声。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/c7200f83.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>另一个高三学生网友的心声。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/8cb89ef6.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>第三个高三学生的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/07902ff0.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有网友说自己的孩子一天只靠着半个玉米过活。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/51734585.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>有西宁网友说自家的门里外都被锁了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/35cea235.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这对祖孙则让人难过了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/ecf55a0b.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>看着这样的心声，我也只能写出来，让其他的西宁朋友们能看到，这样的心声值得被倾听，这样的情绪值得被感受到。</p>\n<p>这就是我在写这文时候的一点想法。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://keep.cdt.media/assets/images/8/2/827966cc/04e2e85f.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[45870,38917,41492,43134,45438,45443],"tags":[45196,45212,46114,44442]}